stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> IDLE
    IDLE --> CONTEXT_CREATED: optimize request
    CONTEXT_CREATED --> MDL_HELD: binder already owns MDL tickets
    MDL_HELD --> DICT_PINNED: pin table definitions
    DICT_PINNED --> STATS_SNAPSHOT: open immutable statistics snapshot
    STATS_SNAPSHOT --> OPTIMIZING: enumerate plans
    OPTIMIZING --> TRACE_WRITING: record optimizer trace
    TRACE_WRITING --> PLAN_READY: physical plan selected
    PLAN_READY --> RELEASE_SNAPSHOT: close stats snapshot
    RELEASE_SNAPSHOT --> RETURNED: return plan to executor
    RETURNED --> IDLE

    OPTIMIZING --> ABORTED: timeout, killed, unsupported feature
    ABORTED --> RELEASE_SNAPSHOT: cleanup
    IDLE --> [*]

    note right of OPTIMIZING
        Optimizer holds metadata pins and immutable statistics only.
        It must not hold row locks, page latches, MTR latches,
        redo wait slots, or physical file locks.
    end note

    note right of TRACE_WRITING
        Trace buffer is session scoped.
        Trace writes do not call storage engine or DD repository.
    end note

